    "faq_FVRtcA": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "question_6H9ftk": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is a cruiser electric bike?",
            "title_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>A cruiser electric bike is built for relaxed, upright riding with comfort-first geometry—ideal for city cruising, casual rides, and everyday trips. Our cruiser lineup is designed for smooth, confidence-forward riding on typical urban routes and weekend outings. </p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_LmwUiG": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Are cruiser ebikes good for commuting?",
            "title_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>Yes. Cruiser ebikes are a great fit for commuting when you want a comfortable posture, steady handling, and an easy daily ride. If you’re riding to work, running errands, or doing short-to-mid city trips, a cruiser-style ebike keeps things simple and comfortable. </p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_qwqGPk": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I choose the best cruiser ebike for my riding style?",
            "title_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>Start with your use case:<br/>● <strong>Daily commuting + quick errands</strong>: look for simple comfort and visibility features.<br/>● <strong>Easier mounting / relaxed posture</strong>: choose a step-through cruiser design (like <a href=\"https://www.jasionbike.com/products/jasion%C2%AEeb5-st-roamer-ebike\" title=\"https://www.jasionbike.com/products/jasion%C2%AEeb5-st-roamer-ebike\">Roamer ST</a>).<br/>● <strong>Weekend rides + touring vibes</strong>: consider the Road Trip option for a more trip-ready setup. </p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_m6DNjd": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How far can a cruiser ebike go on a single charge?",
            "title_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>Range depends on terrain, rider weight, temperature, wind, and assist level. In our cruiser lineup, <a href=\"https://www.jasionbike.com/products/jasion%C2%AEeb5-roamer-ebike\" target=\"_blank\">EB5 Roamer</a> and <a href=\"https://www.jasionbike.com/products/jasion%C2%AEeb5-st-roamer-ebike\" target=\"_blank\">EB5 Roamer ST</a> are listed with a <strong>max range up to 62 miles</strong> and a <strong>48V 11Ah battery</strong>, making them a strong fit for daily commuting and longer weekend rides when you want a comfort-focused cruiser feel. For the best real-world range, use a moderate PAS level, keep tires properly inflated, and plan extra buffer for hills or higher speeds. </p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_JCzLY7": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How fast do cruiser ebikes go, and can I adjust assist levels?",
            "title_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>Our <a href=\"https://www.jasionbike.com/products/jasion%C2%AEeb5-roamer-ebike\" target=\"_blank\">EB5 Roamer series</a> is listed with a <strong>max speed up to 28 mph</strong>, and you can fine-tune the ride using <strong>Pedal Assist levels 0–5</strong> to match your comfort and local riding conditions. Both EB5 Roamer and EB5 Roamer ST also include a <strong>thumb throttle</strong> for convenient acceleration when needed. If you’d like to confirm or adjust the number of assist levels on your display, our manual guidance explains how to switch between 3-level and 5-level PAS settings in the device parameters.  </p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        }
